\end_inset

.
 We can re-write this distribution as 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathbb{P}\left(Y^{\left(i\right)}\in\cdot\mid Y_{1}^{\left(i\right)}=\bar{y}^{\left(i\right)},\rho^{\left(i\right)}<1\right)=\mathbb{P}\left(Y^{\left(i\right)}\in\cdot\mid X_{1}^{\left(i\right)*}=\bar{y}^{\left(i\right)},\rho^{\left(i\right)}<1\right)
\]

\end_inset

